# | 84 | NIST 800-171 v2.0.0                              | Disabled |
# | 85 | NIST 800-53 v5.0.0                               | Disabled |
# |              Organizations Guardrails — SCPs                     |
# | 86 | SCP: Deny root user actions                      | Disabled |
# | 87 | SCP: Deny unapproved regions                     | Disabled |
# | 88 | SCP: Deny disabling security services            | Disabled |
# | 89 | SCP: Enforce encryption                          | Disabled |
# | 90 | SCP: Deny public AMI/EBS sharing                 | Disabled |
# | 91 | SCP: Deny leaving organization                   | Disabled |
# | 92 | SCP: Deny deleting VPC flow logs                 | Disabled |
# | 93 | SCP: Deny deactivating MFA / root keys           | Disabled |
